    "description": {
        "@language": "en-US",
        "@value": "\n                Migliaccio, often served at Carnival, is a lemon-ricotta cheesecake with a difference: a base of semolina flour, which makes it lighter than your typical cheesecake.\n                  \n      Featured in: \n      A Family Affair.\u00a0\n   \n\n\n\n              "
    },
